Tuan Xu.

254
00:19:11,910 --> 00:19:12,590
Ada kapal.

255
00:19:35,900 --> 00:19:37,390
Kebetulan sekali,
langsung bertemu.

256
00:19:37,390 --> 00:19:39,180
Sepertinya langit juga
ingin membunuhnya.

257
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:53,200
Ayah, di sini tempatnya.

258
00:19:53,240 --> 00:19:53,960
Cepat lihat.

259
00:19:56,190 --> 00:19:57,390
Pasukan air Qingzhou.

260
00:19:59,280 --> 00:20:00,550
