Abaikan saja orang dari
Makam Pedang.

275
00:20:58,950 --> 00:21:01,520
Saat dia tiba, Xu Fengnian
sudah mati duluan.

276
00:21:02,590 --> 00:21:03,560
Bendera kapal berhenti.

277
00:21:03,620 --> 00:21:05,520
Dua kapal di kiri dan kanan,
serang kapal musuh.

278
00:21:05,520 --> 00:21:06,720
Jangan biarkan satu pun hidup!

279
00:21:12,390 --> 00:21:13,790
Mereka mengincar kita.

280
00:21:17,480 --> 00:21:18,960
Hentikan kapal!

281
00:21:24,390 --> 00:21:25,590
Gulung bendera!

282
00:21:37,630 --> 00:21:39,310
Untuk apa tongkat besar itu?

283
